+# Meta Note - Step 014 Exploration 001
+
+- When the repository already froze an exact-rewrite shortlist, Step 2 should
+  not reopen branch-adjacent families just to make the slate look richer.
+- Keep at least one reserve comparator, but use active slots only for packages
+  that carry a nontrivial claimed route back to the frozen theorem-facing
+  burden.
+- If a family localizes immediately back to the same burden with no sharper
+  candidate-specific structure, keep it as reserve or reject it rather than
+  spending an active audit slot on it.
