+# Meta Note - Step 014 Exploration 002
+
+- For exact-rewrite audits on a frozen LEI target, derive the native equation
+  first and then force it back through the inherited localized bad term; do not
+  let the native variable choose a different theorem-facing object.
+- Record debt at the first localization step, not after a hoped-for gain has
+  already been narrated.
+- Distinguish "acts on the full burden after reconstruction" from "acts natively
+  on the full burden"; that gap is often the real exchange problem.
