+- `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/MISSION.md`
+
+## Constraints
+
+- Stay inside the inherited suitable-weak / Leray-Hopf + LEI floor.
+- Keep the shared CKN-style cutoff protocol fixed.
+- Do not run the formal anti-repackaging classifier.
+- Do not widen the slate beyond two active plus one reserve.
